channel.title: Cleaned Project Czar V2.0 RELEASE - [350kb Client.java] [1.66mb Overall]
channel.description:
[i]I've finally finished cleaning Czar fully, mostly in the client class, but alot in other classes too. If you find anything else in it I can clean/remove, please tell me as I can't really find anything else to clean ;).
It's taken me something like a week to do this, I've done about 30 mins work every night, with LOADS of help from my friend, Rowin.[/i]
[u][b]Features[/b][/u]
[ul][li]Client.java is 350Kb - Was 930Kb when I started.[/li] [li]There are now 19 Classes, before I started there were 28.[/li] [li]The items now load from a .dat file.[/li] [li]All files have been sorted and put into the right place.[/li] [li]NPC Emotes are now Handled from a .CFG file.[/li] [li]Removed ALL Skills, since they were rubbish anyway, I might make a next version in which I add my own versions of skills into it.[/li] [li]Removed all NPC's apart from a few in Lumbridge.[/li] [li]Cleaned out 3/4 of the processing method in the client class, which proves to reduce alot of 'lag'.[/li] [li]NPCHandler is totally cleaned out, and is now 14.8Kb.[/li] [li]There are now only 4 Sub-Folders.[/li] [li]The secondary saving to .dat in the 'savedgames' folder has been removed, because it had no use at all.[/li] [li]Added my own custom thieving, which is only one method.[/li] [li]Moved ALOT of the integers and single line booleans to either the bottom of client.java, or into player.java.[/li] [li]Removed all unnecessary classes, such as item4, SaveGameHandler, etc.[/li] [li]OVERALL, the source is now 1.66Mb, and before I started cleaning it, it was 4.78Mb.[/li] [li]Very basic PvP combat (Player Vs Player).[/li][/ul]
Failing at thieving:
[img]http://i273.photobucket.com/albums/jj218/primadude/thievefail.jpg[/img]
Succeeding at thieving:
[img]http://i273.photobucket.com/albums/jj218/primadude/thievesuccess.jpg[/img]
Basic combat:
[img]http://i273.photobucket.com/albums/jj218/primadude/combat.jpg[/img]
And I did this Ftw lol:
[img]http://i273.photobucket.com/albums/jj218/primadude/dialogue.jpg[/img]
Download: [url=http://dodownload.filefront.com/12210531//af0c908c66e7148377554decaff989494a2f93f6aef0e1f0965b2276e5aff4db3755ef653a7e2d3f]Click Here[/url].
Enjoy ;)
